fields.name: CounterKey
fields.description: The Key value of the Counter. Must not be empty.

fields.name: PeriodEndTime
fields.description: The date of the end of Counter Period. The date conforms to the following format: `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ` as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.

fields.name: PeriodKey
fields.description: Identifier of the Period for which the counter was collected. Must not be empty.

fields.name: PeriodStartTime
fields.description: The date of the start of Counter Period. The date conforms to the following format: `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ` as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.
